---
title: Quick Sesame-Crusted Salmon with Ginger-Soy Veggies
description: The key to perfectly cooked salmon is crispy skin and a melt-in-your-mouth fillet, and you’ll get all that and more with this
recipe. The veggies are brought to life with a classic soy and ginger combo too. Delish!

*Keep an eye out...Due to recent sourcing challenges, we’ve replaced Asian greens with baby spinach, which may be a little different to what’s pictured. Don’t worry, your recipe will be just as delicious!*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/quick-sesame-crusted-salmon-fd60e573.jpg
